[IMAGE]
Three images showing different perspectives of the property:
1. Side view of the building with a narrow driveway and adjacent residential properties.
1. Rear view showing a parking area with several vehicles.
1. Close-up of the building's utility meters mounted on the exterior wall.
[/IMAGE]

[IMAGE]
Image of a stairwell with brick walls and mailboxes on the right side. The stairwell has a carpeted floor and metal railings.
[/IMAGE]

[IMAGE]
Image of a hallway with a wooden door and a painting on the wall. The floor is carpeted, and there is a metal railing.
[/IMAGE]

[IMAGE]
Image of a brick apartment building exterior with a red awning over the entrance. The building has multiple windows and a concrete pathway leading to the entrance.
[/IMAGE]

[IMAGE]
Image of a stairwell with a painting on the wall. The stairwell has carpeted steps and metal railings.
[/IMAGE]
